room_title: Escape room "International Thief" by Ace of Escape in Tucson
room_description:
A genius engineer turned gem thief is on the loose. He's disappeared and left clues for his lover to find him. You must break into his private office and search through his maps, notebooks and travel memorabilia to find the plane ticket, cash and key he left behind. Using your sleuthing skills, you'll have 60 minutes to get through the room.
Upon request, the room can be modified for kids ages 8 to 13.
